      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver despite showing clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some faded paint on the hood, and a few small dents, while the interior shows typical wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it remains sound and has been regularly serviced, making it a dependable choice for someone prioritizing utility over cosmetics.",
