    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project or a budget-friendly way to get on the road? This car is the perfect canvas for someone who loves to roll up their sleeves and bring a vehicle back to its former glory! While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a great foundation for a dedicated hobbyist or anyone looking for a low-cost entry into car ownership. It\u2019s a diamond in the rough waiting for the right person to give it some TLC!",
